

    ***************  Employee Service CRUD Implementation using AWS - Version : 2.0.1  *******************

Technologies Used : Java 17, Spring Boot, Microservices, Hibernate
AWS Services used : EC2 Instances, S3, Launch Templates, Volumes, Security Groups, Elastic IPs, Load Balancers,
                    Target Groups, Auto Scaling Groups, Elastic Beanstalk (Deployments), CodeBuild (Build),
                    CodePipeline (CI/CD - Pipeline), Simple Notification Service (SNS - EMail Service for
                    Manual Approval)


    //***********  REST API Call *********************//

    # Tomcat Default Port
    Public Facing Port - 8080 : http://localhost:8080/rest-api-employee-services/getEmployeeServicesDeployments
                                http://localhost:8080/rest-api-employee-services/getEmployeeDetails

    # Employee Service Default Port
	Private Facing Port - 9000 : http://localhost:9000/rest-api-employee-services/getEmployeeServicesDeployments
	                             http://localhost:9000/rest-api-employee-services/getEmployeeDetails


    //***********  AWS Microservice API Call *********************//

    # AWS Elastic Beanstalk Default Port
    Public Facing Port - 5000 : http://localhost:5000/rest-api-employee-services/getEmployeeServicesDeployments
                                http://localhost:5000/rest-api-employee-services/getEmployeeDetails















